node.text:
This week’s theme is “Throwback”! Which of these throwback videos was your favorite shoot?

Crazy to think I’ve been taking pictures of strangers for almost 2 years already!

Strangers:
Video 1: @joleendiaz @meilanikalei 
Video 2: @ihaveneverbeentomars 
Video 3: @sophiadamato 
Video 5: @kamrylorin 

Be sure to check out my new account for social media tips: @alexstemp 

#Kdpeoplegallery #portraitpage #endlessfaces #yourvisiongallery #portrait_mf #ig_muse #portraitkillers #portraitsfromtheworld #portraitperfection #dynamicportraits #xelfies #pr0ject_soul #portraitvisuals #featurecreature #wmportraits #portraitsquad #portrait_society #photopeoplegallery #ofhumans #portraitsvisuals #portvisual #feature_portraits #portraitbliss #portzfired #visualportraits #senseports #portraitenvy #theportraitmission

node.text:
Giving strangers Special Effects Makeovers with @makeuppbyruthie. Which makeover was your favorite?

Usually I don’t show all the rejections that I face in filming my content for you guys, but this time I showed every rejection I encountered to film these two photoshoots. Hope you enjoy seeing that part!

What should we transform a stranger into next?

Strangers are @kennacolee and @acidgumibears 
Behind the scenes by @thevidkid1
Smoke bombs by @smoky.bombs 
Dress by @andrea_leo_couture

Street photography in Las Vegas! Which shoot was your favorite?

node.text:
This episode features 3 amazingly talented creators each of which amassed millions of followers within less than a year!

Creator 1: @jakefellman 
Jake is a 3D artist that has amassed 5 million YouTube followers in a matter of half a year using his creativity in short form videos.

Creator 2: @itsdanielmac 
Daniel Mac has grown over 10 million followers by asking one question! He was able to leave his 9 to 5 job to do content creation full time.

Creator 3: @iamtiagz 
Tiagz has an inspirational story where he posted 701 videos that all flopped. His next video went viral and since then his life transformed with over 5 million followers and getting signed by Epic Records.

node.text:
This episode is titled “Jokers” and highlights three cosplayers I was able to find walking around Hollywood Blvd. Which photoshoot was your favorite?

The first video went mega viral on TikTok with nearly 60 million views so I called back Joker and Batman for a follow-up shoot. 

The third video was the first Joker I found and the first time I shot cosplay. It also went very viral on TikTok with almost 40 million views.

Which Joker is your favorite?

Video 1 and 2:
Joker = @agentsofkhaos 
Batman = @lucidluminos 

Video 3:
Joker = @mrjjoker369 

Smoke bombs by @smoky.bombs 
Behind the scenes by @jessbillings_ @jake.ceja

Joker vs Joker: Part 1🃏The results will be released tomorrow! The Jokers are @mrjjoker369 and @agentsofkhaos.

I met each of these Jokers individually at separate times while doing street photography on Hollywood Blvd. They have been fan favorites so I thought it would be fun to do a Joker shootout!

There is so much footage and photos that I had to post this one in two parts, I appreciate your patience it will be worth it!

In the meantime check out my new page for social media tips @alexstemp 

Huge shoutout to my girlfriend for filming this 5 hour photoshoot for us @jessbillings

Avery’s results are on: @averymoore444. Me and one of my followers gave a stranger a photo and video shoot! Which photo was your favorite?

About a week ago one of my followers approached me on the street and told me I was a huge inspiration. He is an aspiring videographer and when I saw his work I saw a lot of potential! I decided to invite him to do a shoot with me and this was the result! Hope you guys enjoyed and if you ever see me on the street come say hi, I want to help the aspiring content creators out there if I can!

The stranger in this video is @ciarakhuerta 

Check out my new page for social media tips @alexstemp

I gave a stranger a princess dress photoshoot #withGalaxy! Which photo was your favorite?

I am pleased to announce that I have partnered up with @SamsungMobileUSA and I am officially #TeamGalaxy. This partnership means a lot to me because I want to inspire people who don't have a camera, or can't afford one, that they can still be a photographer and take stunning portraits! 

This photoshoot was done using the #GalaxyS21Ultra 5G phone, shot in portrait mode! Let me know if you have any questions about mobile photography!

Part 2 of 2: Finding the Joker his Harley Quinn. Which photo is your favorite?Check out Part 1 if you missed it!

This concept was to find a stranger to model and cosplay as Harley Quinn for my friend the Joker @agentsofkhaos. We only had a couple days to put this together so the costume we got was not the best, but we made it work!

Who should we cosplay a stranger as next?

Joker: @agentsofkhaos 
MUA: @fancyflutie 
Harley: @josiiebabie 
Smoke: @smoky.bombs

We transformed a complete stranger into the Grim Reaper and gave him a photoshoot! 

This is Part 3 of transforming strangers with SFX Makeovers! What or who should we transform a stranger into next?

The SFX makeup artist is @fancyflutie and the stranger is @elia_rahemi 

BTS by @jessbillings and smoke bombs by @smoky.bombs 

Check out my new Instagram page solely for social media tips: @alexstemp

node.text:
Warning ⚠️ This photoshoot got a little steamy! Which shot was your favorite?

I found a car wash couples photoshoot while browsing Pinterest by @mollgrune and had to surprise a couple with this photoshoot. 

I met @adrian_e_flores and @143jasmineflores as they were on their weekly bike ride to the beach that they always make time for. It took just a little convincing but they were up for the spontaneous photoshoot and did an amazing job with the shoot!

BTS by @jessbillings 

My new social media tips page: @alexstemp

Usually I don’t show all the rejections that I face in filming my content for you guys, but this time I showed every rejection I encountered to film these two photoshoots. Hope you enjoy seeing that part!
